156
00:08:23,904 --> 00:08:26,038
Kikuoka: Kikuoka in subcon.
Talk to me.

157
00:08:26,106 --> 00:08:29,774
Man: Hello, sir. I know
I'm not supposed to call hq

158
00:08:29,776 --> 00:08:31,176
unless it's important.

159
00:08:31,178 --> 00:08:33,645
