it's some kind of prank.

162
00:08:38,185 --> 00:08:40,919
A couple visitors
just showed up at our location

163
00:08:40,987 --> 00:08:42,387
without an appointment.

164
00:08:42,389 --> 00:08:45,257
Kikuoka: Visitors?
Who are they, clients?

165
00:08:45,325 --> 00:08:48,060
Hiraki: No, they're
definitely not clients,

166
00:08:48,128 --> 00:08:50,062
but they seem to know
a lot about us.

167
00:08:50,130 --> 00:08:52,797
