two teenage girls.

168
00:08:52,867 --> 00:08:53,866
Higa and Kikuoka: What?!

169
00:08:53,934 --> 00:08:55,600
Kikuoka: Teenagers, you said?

170
00:08:55,669 --> 00:08:56,601
Hiraki: Yeah.

171
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:58,871
Anyway, they knew your name

172
00:08:58,939 --> 00:09:01,005
and that you were at rath hq,
so I let them in.

173
00:09:01,007 --> 00:09:02,807
They said I should call you

174
00:09:02,809 --> 00:09:04,609
