to check the f.L.A. Rate

175
00:09:04,678 --> 00:09:06,679
of the Underworld,
said it was urgent.

176
00:09:06,747 --> 00:09:07,646
( Higa gasps )

177
00:09:09,950 --> 00:09:10,883
Holy...

178
00:09:10,951 --> 00:09:13,151
