you'd know who they were.

185
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:25,898
Hold on. I wrote them down.

186
00:09:25,966 --> 00:09:28,901
Let's see.
One called herself "Sinon,"

187
00:09:28,969 --> 00:09:30,769
and the other, "Leafa."

188
00:09:30,837 --> 00:09:33,638
