what they told me to tell you.

189
00:09:33,707 --> 00:09:34,573
( Both gasp )

190
00:09:42,149 --> 00:09:44,549
Klein: I swear. He's in a coma,

191
00:09:44,618 --> 00:09:48,753
and he still managed to get
caught up in something crazy.

192
00:09:48,755 --> 00:09:51,156
I mean,
a full-on A.I. Called Alice

193
00:09:51,225 --> 00:09:54,626
who was born in a virtual world
made by the sdf?

194
00:09:54,695 --> 00:09:57,562
( Groans )
This is way beyond v.R. Games,

195
00:09:57,631 --> 00:09:59,364
and there's no goin' back.

196
00:09:59,366 --> 00:10:01,766
Silica: Poor Alice.
She's so special,

197
00:10:01,768 --> 00:10:03,768
