to fly fighter jets.

198
00:10:03,838 --> 00:10:06,839
Yui: Ultimately, yes,
but they won't right away.

199
00:10:06,907 --> 00:10:08,173
Rath will probably use her

200
00:10:08,242 --> 00:10:11,109
to demonstrate the technology
to the world first.

201
00:10:11,178 --> 00:10:14,179
The hijackers aboard
the ocean turtle, however,

202
00:10:14,181 --> 00:10:16,715
