for what she was intended.

205
00:10:20,387 --> 00:10:22,320
Klein: Know anything else
about those creeps,

206
00:10:22,389 --> 00:10:24,322
like who they are
or where they're from?

207
00:10:24,391 --> 00:10:26,058
Yui: I can't confirm it,

208
00:10:26,126 --> 00:10:29,794
but I think they're
U.S. military or intelligence.

209
00:10:29,796 --> 00:10:30,663
- ( Group gasps )
- Klein: What?!

210
00:10:30,731 --> 00:10:31,930
Lisbeth: They're behind it?!

211
00:10:31,998 --> 00:10:33,998
O-Oh, my god.

212
00:10:34,068 --> 00:10:37,069
Yui: Again, I can't confirm
they're involved with this,

213
00:10:37,137 --> 00:10:41,740
but if they are and Alice
does fall into their hands,

214
00:10:41,808 --> 00:10:43,341
