want that to happen to her,

216
00:10:48,749 --> 00:10:50,215
because Alice--

217
00:10:50,284 --> 00:10:52,150
Alice is proof!

218
00:10:52,219 --> 00:10:54,753
Her existence proves
all v.R. Worlds,

219
00:10:54,821 --> 00:10:56,755
starting with "s.A.O.,"
are real,

220
00:10:56,823 --> 00:10:59,157
that those who lived in them
had real lives!

221
00:10:59,226 --> 00:11:02,227
She's the result of massive
amounts of the time, energy,

222
00:11:02,229 --> 00:11:05,830
and imagination
of thousands of humans!

223
00:11:05,832 --> 00:11:09,234
( All gasp )

224
00:11:09,303 --> 00:11:12,036
Yui: I'm convinced
beyond a doubt

225
00:11:12,106 --> 00:11:15,741
she's why the seed package
was created, its true purpose...

226
00:11:16,911 --> 00:11:19,244
To give birth
to someone like her.

227
00:11:19,313 --> 00:11:21,379
Throughout all
the connected worlds

228
00:11:21,448 --> 00:11:23,115
that sprang up from the seed,

229
00:11:23,183 --> 00:11:26,919
so many people have laughed,
cried, suffered, and loved.

230
00:11:26,987 --> 00:11:29,053
It was the radiance
of all those souls

231
00:11:29,123 --> 00:11:31,256
