that made it possible

232
00:11:31,325 --> 00:11:35,394
for a new form of humanity
to be born in the Underworld.

233
00:11:35,462 --> 00:11:37,062
Daddy and mommy,

234
00:11:37,131 --> 00:11:42,000
Leafa, Klein, Lisbeth,
Silica, Agil, and Sinon,

235
00:11:42,069 --> 00:11:45,137
it's the combination of
your hearts and so many others,

236
00:11:45,205 --> 00:11:47,472
all woven together
in a big tapestry,

237
00:11:47,474 --> 00:11:49,141
that gave birth to Alice!

238
00:11:51,211 --> 00:11:53,278
Lisbeth: Yeah, you're right.

239
00:11:53,347 --> 00:11:55,414
It's all connected,

240
00:11:55,482 --> 00:11:59,017
people and time
and our hearts, too,

241
00:11:59,086 --> 00:12:01,219
flowin' like a big river.

242
00:12:01,288 --> 00:12:02,287
Yui: Eh?

243
00:12:02,289 --> 00:12:04,089
Silica: It's okay, Yui.

244
00:12:04,158 --> 00:12:05,824
Don't cry.

245
00:12:05,892 --> 00:12:08,093
We'll rescue kirito and Asuna.

246
00:12:08,162 --> 00:12:12,164
I promise, we'll do whatever it
takes to get them out of this.

247
00:12:12,232 --> 00:12:14,232
You can count on that.

248
00:12:14,301 --> 00:12:15,634
Klein: Damn straight.

249
00:12:15,702 --> 00:12:17,102
You should have
come to us sooner.

250
00:12:17,171 --> 00:12:19,037
If there's a chance
to get 'em out,

251
00:12:19,106 --> 00:12:20,505
hell, we're taking it.

252
00:12:20,507 --> 00:12:21,774
Agil: You got that right.

253
00:12:21,842 --> 00:12:23,508
